high_descs: Turn around and head towards the sink on your right.
Pick up the knife that is in front of the plate.
Turn right and towards the sink on your left.
Slice the tomato in the sink.
Place the knife next to the tomato in the sink.
Pick up a slice of tomato from the sink.
Turn right and head towards the microwave on your right.
Open the microwave, place the slice tomato in it, heat it up, and take the slice tomato out of microwave.
Turn right and head towards the sink on your right.
Place the slice tomato back into the sink.
anns.task_desc: Heat up a piece of slice tomato.

high_descs: Turn around, then turn right at the left side of the sink.
Pick up the knife in front of the plate.
Turn right, then turn left to face the sink basin.
Slice the tomato in the sink.
Put the knife in the sink.
Take a tomato slice from the sink.
Turn right, go straight, then turn right to approach the microwave.
Cook the tomato slice in the microwave.
Go right, then turn right to return to the sink basin.
Put the tomato slice in the sink basin, in front of the tomato.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked tomato slice in the sink.

high_descs: turn around and walk over to the sink on the right side
grab a knife from the sink
move to the right a bit and face the sink again
slice up the tomato pepper inside of the sink
place the knife inside of the sink
grab a pepper slice from inside of the sink
turn around and walk to the microwave on the left side of the room
place the pepper slice inside of the microwave, microwave it, and then take it back out
turn around and walk back over to the sink on the other side of the room
place the pepper slice inside of the microwave
anns.task_desc: place a microwaved pepper slice inside of the sink
